quests.desc: It's time to explore the amazing world of TextWorld! Here is how to play! First of all, go to the south. With that accomplished, venture south. After that, head west. Once you succeed at that, make an effort to go west. After that, attempt to go to the south. Then, make an attempt to go to the east. And then, head east. That done, go south. Once you finish that, try to venture west. Once you manage that, take the loaf of bread in the studio. Once that's all handled, you can stop!

objective: You are now playing a fast paced session of TextWorld! Here is how to play! First off, if it's not too much trouble, I need you to attempt to take a trip south. And then, try to go south. With that accomplished, make an effort to go to the west. With that done, attempt to move west. Then, make an effort to travel south. And then, make an attempt to go to the east. And then, head east. That done, travel south. With that accomplished, venture west. And then, pick up the loaf of bread from the studio. That's it!
